unittitle_ssm: New York University Archives Collection of Yearbooks
abstract_ssm: This collection contains yearbooks dating from 1887 to 2012 issued by New York University and its component schools. These yearbooks typically document graduating seniors (with portraits), administrators and faculty, clubs and other student organizations, and athletics. The collection also contains registers of incoming freshmen for certain schools. While the collection is extensive, it is not comprehensive, and there may be published yearbooks that are not included in this collection.
